data.description: Beautiful brick front colonial on a cul-de-sac lot.  First floor home office with built-in shelves & hardwood floors, kitchen with granite counters, island, recessed lighting, SS appliances including gas cooktop, double oven, plus walk-in pantry. Huge family room off kitchen w/hardwood floors, new wood stove with stone surround, & crown molding, mud room off garage w/California Closet built-ins (4 lockers!), separate dining room & living room, both with crown molding, tiered deck off family room overlooking the large backyard. Four foot extension on two levels. Upstairs you'll find a huge primary suite with a sitting room, 2 walk-in closets both with California Closet built-ins, barn door to primary bath with soaking tub, 2 vanities, separate shower.  3 additional bedrooms including guest room w/private bath & huge closet and separate hall bath.  CC built-ins in 2 of those bedrooms.  Fully finished basement with spacious rec room, home gym (equipment conveys), another room used as a 5th bedroom, full bath with jetted tub, and 2 storage areas, plus walkup stairs to backyard. Over .3 acre lot with irrigation system! Roof and HVAC replaced in 2016. Close to Rt 97, BWI, shopping.
